race.description: Summerset Park Stud F&M Maiden Plate
race.comment: OAK PARK MADDISON (10) has been about the money with two minor placings from four starts this campaign, the latest a solid third over 1500m at Gawler. Well-placed and looks hard to beat. GOODLOOKIN' GURU (9) was good on debut here 11 days ago when chasing gamely into the placings. Is sure to have come on from that and is drawn to get all the favours again. Can go one better this time. PRETTY MORSEL (6) hit the frame two starts ago at Morphettville but ran below par last time when sixth at Morphettville Parks after being prominent at the turn. Peak fitness now and keeps Crowther from a good draw. Have to consider. SPLASH OF WHITE (7) led early and was still in the firing line on the turn before tiring to finish sixth here last time out. Can give backers another sight in front. YOU'RESOGOLDEN (12) debut for the Hickmott camp and has trialled well in readiness. Will pay to monitor the market.
